Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:17686,20686}One, two, three!\NOne, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:24286,26286}What did you want\Nto talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:29386,32286}Well, I think I have a rough idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:33052,35752}I can't go out with you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:38519,40519}Rumi loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:40519,42952}I am the reason\Nwhy she has changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:42952,45819}It wasn't the infection that did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:45819,48819}it's because\NI had never given up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50119,53719}I will kill you.\NI've always loved him, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:53719,55052}If only you didn't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:55519,59986}If I refuse to date you,\NRumi might become normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:60519,62886}But if I don't, she'll get even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:62886,65552}No matter what you say,\Nmy feeling doesn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:67552,69886}Can you guess\Nwhat I'm thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:72352,76319}I'm not sure what I want more,\Nto slap you or to drag you to that warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:77419,80286}I told you before.\NI won't be scared by Rumi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:80686,84686}I'm not the type\Nthat suppresses his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84686,86652}Let's be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86652,91152}I can't imagine her getting better\Njust because we don't go out with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91152,94452}I'll try once more to convince Rumi\Nto go to the hospital with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94952,99286}We'll handle this between ourselves.\NThank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99686,101186}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101186,103886}I've made my mind.\NI'll pass on slapping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103886,105852}S… Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108852,111519}Stop it. Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112652,116452}I will, if you say you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121352,122919}It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128919,130652}Kobayakawa!\NWhere did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130652,131819}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133652,135319}It's Rumi's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135319,138486}What is she doing with\NCaptain Ishikura of the men's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139219,141752}What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141752,144152}Ishikura-san, do you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144152,146319}Wait, weren't you with Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146319,147852}That's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147852,149619}So, do you like me not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149619,150986}No… Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157152,158619}{\i1}What is it about, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162752,164486}What the heck?\NWhy did you bite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164486,166519}Assemble on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166852,168619}They're calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168619,173486}I'd like you to explain later\Nwhy you made a move on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178252,182152}I really don't know\Nwhat to make of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182486,183652}Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183652,189019}It's good if she stays with Ishikura.\NAll the better for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189019,191119}That's not what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191586,194319}Rumi has eyes only for you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194652,197786}We haven't finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197786,199586}Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199586,200752}Do you dislike me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203386,204186}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206486,208152}I like you. A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209786,210986}You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213519,214686}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214686,218252}It's better if Rumi\Ndoesn't see us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218252,219686}I'll leave later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224319,228986}One, two! Three, four!\NOne, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228986,231486}You're late!\NWhere've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231486,233886}– You set a bad example for the freshmen.\N– I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233886,236386}After you warm up, we'll clock you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236386,237552}You're going after Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237552,238886}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245286,247352}Sir, where's Captain Ishikura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247786,250852}Ah, he was just here but he felt sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253152,254119}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254119,256419}Ruka, I'm starting the timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256419,257719}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267152,268686}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269486,270919}How was it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270919,273619}You really are twins.\NEven your timings are identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274386,277519}I recently noticed Rumi has had\Nvery uneven times for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277519,279352}but I now see it's the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280119,282719}Well, you two\Nhad a lot going on lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282719,284686}There's nothing we can do\Nabout your bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284686,286252}Sir, let me take a look\Nat it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287652,289586}{\i1}He's right, they're very uneven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289586,292652}{\i1}Now they're the worst.\NThey were the best at…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293019,294152}{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302119,305319}{\i1}It overlaps with the time\NI floated in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314886,318386}{\i1}It was at peak in the middle of\Nthe last month and the worst the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318386,320352}{\i1}And this month\Nit's exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322252,324552}At first, I thought it was\Njust a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324552,326019}But this is not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328886,331186}Rumi has hinted that\Nshe killed Asako-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337252,339286}Has she lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.78,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341786,344786}Both events occurred at full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344786,346852}Are our powers the strongest\Nat the full moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347419,349352}Rumi didn't do anything\Non any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350686,352219}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352219,356819}I don't get it, but what I do get is that\Nsoon Rumi will get violent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358419,360686}I applaud you, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361919,362819}Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362819,364352}You're not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364352,367786}Rest assured, it's not full moon yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367786,369952}I don't have the power to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369952,372886}So it really has to do\Nwith the phases of the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373086,374819}Not just the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374819,379619}I think what Touma-senpai said\Nis probably true.{NOTE:xxx}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381852,385852}But yes, as full moon approaches,\NI feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385852,388686}Something is going on with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388686,391586}I can feel the power\Nflowing through all of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392419,395619}With the new moon,\NI can only do as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395619,397552}I can't even go through objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398186,400519}What about you, Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403586,406186}From your reaction I'm guessing\Nthat my powers are stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406419,407819}Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407819,409386}What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414019,415819}You don't like me\Nin the same room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415819,417819}I'll leave you alone for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418719,419986}Rumi…
