Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493786,495686}Wait up, Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497119,499219}Rumi, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499219,501986}Please, let's get to the hospital\Nand see that doctor once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501986,503419}Okay, Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503419,504386}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504386,505419}Ah, thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505419,506919}I'll let the club adviser know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511019,513452}Ruka, can we take a small detour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513452,515319}Sure. Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515619,517619}For shopping. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523052,525719}Rumi, were there any shops\Nin this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539819,540652}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541252,543619}Rumi. What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543886,545952}Don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545952,549552}I told you that I don't have\Nthe power to kill you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550386,552752}But… I can feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553952,555519}Come on, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558586,559419}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560119,562386}S-Someone…\NSomeone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567752,569186}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572719,574219}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578086,580252}As much as I want to kill you, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580252,581919}So I asked him to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582452,584586}W-Wait! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588019,590019}Captain is floating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590886,592952}I've been doing some experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592952,594852}I got him infected with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594852,597786}Infected? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597986,601752}And this is where the fun begins.\NI can control him as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601752,604752}Ishikura-san,\Ndo with Ruka as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605986,608186}Make sure she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609952,611086}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611719,612919}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612919,614119}Hurry, after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627052,629619}Ishikura-san, she's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630119,632952}No! Make him stop!\NRumi, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633819,635919}Don't worry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635919,639552}You don't want to see Katsuyuki-san\Nafter being held by another man, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640052,642486}This time will be your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653152,654486}Touma-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655152,657219}Ishikura!\NWhat the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657219,660086}Ishikura-san, kill Ruka at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660386,661419}Ishikura, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661419,662786}I'm not letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662786,666252}Stay away! Stay away, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670752,673119}Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676286,679019}Help me! Someone save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684586,685286}Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705719,707352}Don't look!\NDon't look, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707852,708919}Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708919,709986}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709986,712552}Call the police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712552,713319}Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728452,732986}Senpai… Thank you\Nfor not talking about Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733519,738352}For better or worse,\Nthe witnesses couldn't see Rumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738352,742652}But if Ishikura was being\Nmanipulated by Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742652,744986}We shouldn't hide this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745286,747519}As it is, Ishikura alone\Nwill be held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747519,750419}Yeah. I don't intend\Nto remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750419,753019}I'll try talking\Nto Mom and Dad once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753019,756886}If I wait until full moon and show them\Nmy powers, they will believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757219,761652}Until then, I know it's tough, but go to\Nthe hospital and learn more about this illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761652,762352}Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769152,772252}Excuse me, I came\Nto see Dr. Kaibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773786,774219}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774219,775886}Is Dr. Kaibara here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775886,777419}Please tell him that Touma is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777419,780219}I will.\NPlease wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780519,783286}You must be tired.\NYou look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783286,784719}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784986,789052}We must stop Rumi before school tomorrow\Nnow that she knows how to infect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789052,790186}Kobayakawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790186,791952}Kobayakawa Ruka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791952,793152}Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.11,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:793152,795119}Examination room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797286,798919}Oh? It's you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798919,799452}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799452,801552}Never mind. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801852,805719}I am sorry to ask you the same thing,\Nbut I would like to ask you for a re-examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805719,806986}The infection is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807152,808419}It's spreading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808419,809619}We're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809619,812352}A person close to\NTouma-senpai contracted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812352,814152}Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814152,817152}I will re-examine you like you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817452,819586}Prepare Operating Room 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819586,820252}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820252,822619}Katsuyuki-kun,\Ncould you wait in the lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822852,824486}Of course, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831386,832752}Where is the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834586,836719}Lay down right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836719,837719}On that bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837719,839252}Yes. Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839252,840652}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848719,849619}Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849619,852286}Stay relaxed.\NIt's for the examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855452,858119}I'll be right back.\NWait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862752,865419}Doctor? The room is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865419,867019}Ah, we won't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867219,867719}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867719,868986}The patient's gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868986,871952}I understand.\NI will clean it up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875052,876819}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876819,878486}Could you return this\Nto your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878486,880386}She forgot to leave it\Nat the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880819,883886}She left it in the examination room\Nthe previous time she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884119,885086}Previous time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885086,887719}It was about an hour ago, I think?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900119,901586}What is this injection for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911786,912686}{\i1}It was Rumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912686,914419}{\i1}Rumi was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914419,916386}Ruka… Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922352,924286}Where's Ruka?\NWhere is Kobayakawa Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924552,926619}She went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926619,927752}This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936219,937052}Hands off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941919,943452}– Are you okay, Ruka?\N– Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945686,948386}Shit, she got even Dr. Kaibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949119,951386}No matter.\NLet's get outta here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955119,958386}Rumi wants to infect more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958386,960319}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960619,963319}Don't panic.\NWe'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964686,966286}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966686,969719}I don't think Rumi will try\Nto do anything to me at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972586,974652}Yes. We had enough\Nexcitement for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976052,977186}I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977186,978886}Thank you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981886,982986}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982986,984019}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984019,986686}It's so late, where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986686,988419}I've been worried sick about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988419,991552}The police just called.\NYou poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991552,993286}I'm sorry we're so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993652,997252}She was very stressed,\Nso I tried to calm her down on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997752,1000019}You must've been so scared, Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000019,1002452}A detective will come later\Nto ask you some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002452,1004419}I'll be on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004652,1006852}Thank you, Katsuyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018186,1019686}It's all fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019686,1020752}You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024019,1025652}Mom, where's Rumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026086,1028052}Where is she?\NHas she returned home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028286,1029819}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029819,1031519}Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031519,1036219}{\i1}She went to the hospital,\Nbut where later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038786,1042019}Mom, please,\Nyou've got to listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042019,1044419}I'm just preparing dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044752,1046886}Listen, this is really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046886,1048952}Rumi has murdered somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049486,1052752}I know this is a lot to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053652,1056352}But I'm not lying, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056586,1058186}Not just one. She killed two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058186,1060852}I didn't want to believe it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060852,1063019}It's for real, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063019,1066919}Asako-senpai's killer\Nwas Rumi all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070819,1071819}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073952,1074519}Mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088652,1091219}You're quite obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092286,1094352}When did you do it to Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094852,1096619}Mom, grab Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097686,1099552}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107086,1108086}Dad's bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108752,1110619}Dad's come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112086,1112952}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115752,1118086}Dad can't hear you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123919,1124986}Even Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125386,1127786}Mom, Dad, bring Ruka to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128986,1130452}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130452,1131919}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134286,1137319}Stop it, Dad!\NCan't you recognize me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137319,1139386}Try as much as you want,\Nhe won't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140019,1142319}He only listens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143119,1145386}You'll feel unpleasant for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146452,1147786}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147786,1149352}You'll learn soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150086,1152552}Mom, Dad. Hold her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152552,1153586}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154386,1155886}Rumi, please—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155886,1157186}There. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157186,1159819}There can be only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160186,1162586}Now Katsuyuki-san will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169919,1171086}Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172586,1174586}They can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174586,1176952}Dad, help me take her upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176952,1178419}Mom, answer the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182519,1183852}Yes? Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184152,1186819}I'm sorry, it's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187719,1193219}A few things happened,\Nand we're here to question your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193719,1196352}Ruka is not ready to see anyone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196352,1198152}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198152,1200986}I am afraid I must ask you\Nto let me see her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200986,1202152}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207352,1209986}Don't try anything funny,\Nor you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209986,1211952}It's the police.\NThey want to talk to Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211952,1214486}I'll go instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219252,1221886}Oh, it's good that you're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222152,1225052}I was quite shocked when I heard\Neverything from my wife and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227352,1231819}Let's get to the point. Could you describe\Nthe incident from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236886,1238719}{\i1}I have to get Touma-senpai here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243386,1247752}So you were in the same club\Nas that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247752,1249086}Yes. It was a track and field club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249386,1254286}{\i1}Three… Two… Five… Two… Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258486,1260186}{\i1}Please, answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262352,1265719}I know it's hard, but could you\Ndescribe it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269319,1271052}Yes? This is Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271586,1272552}{\i1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272552,1273652}{\i1}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273652,1275119}{\i1}This is Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275586,1277986}{\i1}Please, Senpai, figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277986,1281886}I don't know anything.\NCaptain Ishikura went crazy all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281886,1283886}I am the victim here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288719,1290252}{\i1}He hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297352,1298186}{\i1}Don't tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298186,1299752}Let's get back to it another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299752,1301719}Sorry for disturbing your evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306286,1308219}{\i1}Senpai… Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317686,1319952}I told you not to try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320552,1322919}It's like talking to a goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323552,1325852}No one is going to come anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326686,1328819}Let's pick up where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331486,1333752}Ruka? Looks like\Nyou want to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334419,1336019}Fine, I'll let you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337652,1339919}Rumi… I hold\Nno grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340419,1342352}But you can, if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350852,1352519}You can't escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352686,1354719}And now, I'll watch you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365519,1367719}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369952,1370652}Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1371186,1372619}Touma-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1375186,1377552}{\i1}Touma-senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391186,1393686}Ruka, this time around\NI really saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393686,1395186}Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396486,1398552}Are you okay, Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398552,1400386}Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400386,1403586}Rumi…\NShe infected Mom and Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404086,1405552}She what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418519,1420919}Listen. I left my bike nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.18,0:23:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1423186,1424719}Ruka, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.68,0:23:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1437686,1438686}That bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439019,1441786}We should be fine now.\NYou can crash at my house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441786,1443619}Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1469019,1470252}{\i1}A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.85,0:24:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1470852,1472219}What's wrong, Ruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.21,0:24:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1472219,1474352}I'm sorry. I woke you up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1474352,1476319}Nah, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1476319,1477986}I couldn't sleep a wink anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.65,0:24:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1478652,1480719}I am afraid to close my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.71,0:24:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1480719,1482386}Soon it'll be full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1483219,1485552}Rumi's power is getting\Nstronger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.55,0:24:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1485552,1487952}What can we possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.21,0:24:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1488219,1489652}I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.65,0:24:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1489652,1490886}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1490886,1492852}Go to sleep.\NDon't think about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.88,0:24:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1494886,1497386}Here, I cast a spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.38,0:24:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1497386,1498786}You'll sleep well tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1509252,1512352}{\i1}I can't say I dislike\Nthe warmth of another human.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.35,0:25:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1512352,1516952}{\i1}I'm used to sleeping,\Nseeing my face next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.95,0:25:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1516952,1522119}{\i1}I was comfortable feeling someone's\Nbreath on me, and I loved the warmth of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.55,0:25:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1524552,1528819}{\i1}Rumi… What on earth\Nis going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.58,0:25:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1529586,1532052}{\i1}Are you really Rumi?
Comment: 0,0:25:38.51,0:25:38.51,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1538519,1538519}Ending
Comment: 0,0:28:09.81,0:28:09.81,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1689819,1689819}Next episode preview
