Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.65,0:28:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1695652,1699019}Rumi, burning with hatred,\Ncontinues to take her vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.01,0:28:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1699019,1705052}For her goal she infected and used two\Nof her classmates, and even her own family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.05,0:28:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1705052,1709419}Ruka is afraid that now that Rumi knows\NKatsuyuki's feelings won't change,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.41,0:28:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1709419,1711619}she will target him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.15,0:28:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1712152,1716852}On the night of the full moon,\NRuka's anger explodes in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.85,0:28:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1716852,1720452}"Darkness of the Sea,\NShadow of the Moon", Volume 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.45,0:28:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1720452,1723586}"The final confrontation".\NPlease look forward to it!
